Medicinal Product

This value set provide an example of possible codes representing Medicinal Products. It is envisioned that IDMP MPID will be used in the next future.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.9.6.1.5
    CodeDisplay
    023108AMOXICILLINA DOC
  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/ndc
    CodeDisplay
    50436-3129'Amoxicillin and Clavulanate Potassium
